  "page": "Daemon Blackfyre (cousin of Maelys I)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For others with the same name, see <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Blackfyre\" title=\"Daemon Blackfyre\">Daemon Blackfyre</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackfyre\" title=\"House Blackfyre\"><img alt=\"House Blackfyre 2.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/House_Blackfyre_2.svg/50px-House_Blackfyre_2.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/House_Blackfyre_2.svg/75px-House_Blackfyre_2.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a3/House_Blackfyre_2.svg/100px-House_Blackfyre_2.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Daemon Blackfyre</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\"><img alt=\"Golden Company.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/50px-Golden_Company.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/75px-Golden_Company.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/100px-Golden_Company.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Maelys_the_monstrous2_by_mike_hallstein-da2emc1.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Maelys the monstrous2 by mike hallstein-da2emc1.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/38/Maelys_the_monstrous2_by_mike_hallstein-da2emc1.png/350px-Maelys_the_monstrous2_by_mike_hallstein-da2emc1.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"531\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/38/Maelys_the_monstrous2_by_mike_hallstein-da2emc1.png/525px-Maelys_the_monstrous2_by_mike_hallstein-da2emc1.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/38/Maelys_the_monstrous2_by_mike_hallstein-da2emc1.png/700px-Maelys_the_monstrous2_by_mike_hallstein-da2emc1.png 2x\" /></a><div><a href=\"/index.php/Maelys_I_Blackfyre\" title=\"Maelys I Blackfyre\">Maelys I Blackfyre</a> killing his cousin, Daemon,<br />by Mike Hallstein ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Captain-general\" title=\"Captain-general\">Captain-general</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackfyre\" title=\"House Blackfyre\">House Blackfyre</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_241_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">241</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_258_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">258&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Daemon Blackfyre</b> was a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackfyre\" title=\"House Blackfyre\">House Blackfyre</a>. He was a cousin of <a href=\"/index.php/Maelys_I_Blackfyre\" title=\"Maelys I Blackfyre\">Maelys I Blackfyre</a> and a <a href=\"/index.php/Captain-general\" title=\"Captain-general\">captain-general</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf416.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf416.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daemon_Blackfyre_(cousin_of_Maelys_I)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Daemon fought with his cousin, <a href=\"/index.php/Maelys_I_Blackfyre\" title=\"Maelys I Blackfyre\">Maelys</a>, over the command of the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a>. Maelys killed Daemon's <a href=\"/index.php/Horse\" title=\"Horse\">destrier</a> with a single punch, and then twisted Daemon's head until he tore it from his shoulders.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf416.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf416.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daemon_Blackfyre_(cousin_of_Maelys_I)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Daemon's descent from his namesake, the <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_I_Blackfyre\" title=\"Daemon I Blackfyre\">first Daemon Blackfyre</a>, is currently unknown.\n</p>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center